# Lychee ignore list — false positives and known-ok external links

# Localhost / dev URLs
http://localhost
https://localhost
http://127.0.0.1

# Fonts and external CDNs (rate-limited, flaky in CI)
https://fonts.googleapis.com
https://fonts.gstatic.com

# Social media (aggressive bot detection)
https://www.linkedin.com
https://twitter.com
https://x.com
https://www.instagram.com
https://www.facebook.com

# YouTube (bot detection)
https://www.youtube.com
https://youtube.com

# GitHub Actions badges (often rate-limited)
https://github.com/Bygmedai/.*/actions/workflows/.*\.svg
